subject: Re: Transform Your Business with ComplAI
body: Hi, this sounds interesting! Can you tell me more about pricing and how long implementation typically takes?

subject: Re: Excited to Connect!
body:
Hi Johnny,

Thanks for your prompt response! We’re thrilled about your interest in our solutions and can’t wait to dive deeper with you.

To keep the momentum going, how about we set up a call? You can book a time that works best for you via my calendar link: [insert calendar link].

During our conversation, you can expect to learn:

- A detailed breakdown of our pricing packages and how they can be customized for your needs.
- An overview of our implementation timeline and what support you'll receive at each stage.
- Insights into how our solution can significantly streamline your process and deliver value to your team.

Looking forward to connecting soon! Please let me know if you have any specific topics you’d like us to cover during our chat.

Best,
The ComplAI Team
